er und staatlicher Einrichtungen sowie der NSDAP und ihrer Organisationen die jüdischen Sportlerinnen und Sportler betreffend aufgeführt.   aThe voluntary adoption of Aryan-only clauses in many sports clubs as early as 1933 – before the establishment of the National Socialist sports regime – was a first step on the way to the collapse of civilization. The source collection provides a comprehensive overview about the legal processes around the exclusion of Jewish athletes in the 1930s and 40s.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 0aAntisemitism in sportszGermany. 0aAthletic clubszGermanyxHistoryy20th centuryvSources. 0aNational socialism and sports. 4aDiscrimination against Jews. 4aDiskriminierung von Juden. 4aNational Socialism. 4aNationalsozialismus. 4aSport. 4asports. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh1 aPeiffer, Lorenz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWahlig, Henry, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2017z9783110547764oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831105325620 cprintz978311053231940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311053473340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110534733423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110534733.jpg  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017